    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_3780616758" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3780616758" />
    <a title="Elle" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/70046142-elle"><img alt="Elle" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1548160841p2/70046142.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3780616758?book_show_action=true">Jan 18, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Elle" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Elle" href="/user/show/70046142-elle">Elle</a>
      </span>

          marked it as to-read


          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780679403586" href="/book/show/1713631.Dead_Man_Walking">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3780616758" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4441511638691605193">In light of the eleventh-hour federal executions the Trump administration has rushed through at the tail end of his presidency, I’m doing a buddy read of this book by anti-capital punishment activist, Sister Helen Prejean, with my friend <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/45765880-tomes-and-textiles' rel='nofollow noopener'>Carmen</a> over at <a href='https://instagram.com/tomesandtextiles?igshid=s630fth67f4d' rel='nofollow noopener'>@tomesandtextiles</a>!</span>
  <span id="freeText4441511638691605193" style="display:none">In light of the eleventh-hour federal executions the Trump administration has rushed through at the tail end of his presidency, I’m doing a buddy read of this book by anti-capital punishment activist, Sister Helen Prejean, with my friend <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/45765880-tomes-and-textiles" rel="nofollow noopener">Carmen</a> over at <a href="https://instagram.com/tomesandtextiles?igshid=s630fth67f4d" rel="nofollow noopener">@tomesandtextiles</a>!</span>
