<div id="review_3217812922" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3217812922" />
    <a title="Stephanie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/61785501-stephanie"><img alt="Stephanie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1613631315p2/61785501.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3217812922?book_show_action=true">May 12, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Stephanie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Stephanie" href="/user/show/61785501-stephanie">Stephanie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/61785501-stephanie?shelf=school-reads">school-reads</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3217812922" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7036128978502139618">Incredibly insightful. Read it for my school’s English class, and it completely changed the way I view death penalty. Prejean corrects many of the misconceptions of the death penalty in the US and builds a strong argument against it. <br/><br/>Nonfiction isn’t really my cup of tea, hence the 1 star deduction since I felt it was draggy at some points. Otherwise, I enjoyed the narrative portions of the book and the overall information that was provided.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


