          <a href="/book/show/42588467-river-of-fire"><img id="more_book_42588467" alt="River of Fire: My Spiritual Journey" title="River of Fire: My Spiritual Journey" width="50" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1552418251l/42588467._SX98_.jpg" /></a>
